	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Ok, that makes sense, thanks. I thought that must be the case. Perhaps some mention of that should be made in mapper docs or on the wiki, newbies might be completely thrown for a loop by that.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
